---
title: Vegetarian Sausage Cassoulet with Linda McCartney Sausages, Cannellini Beans and Parsley
description: Cassoulet is a rich and hearty dish that is traditionally slow-cooked and made with meat. In this recipe, however, we’ve halved the time and opted for Linda McCartney sausages for a delicious vegetarian treat that’s packed with wholesome flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegetarian-sausage-cassoulet-042d404e-d3713910.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/vegetarian-sausage-cassoulet-5dfca5211413cb766f301737-b2948ec0.pdf
cuisine: French
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
